{"title":"砝码称重 2","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":15,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2144","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>有n个砝码，现在要称一个质量为m的物体，请问最少需要挑出几个砝码来称？</p>\n<p>注意一个砝码最多只能挑一次</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行两个整数n和m，接下来n行每行一个整数表示每个砝码的重量。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出选择的砝码的总数k，你的程序必须使得k尽量的小。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3 10<br>5<br>9<br>1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">2</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1&lt;=n&lt;=30，1&lt;=m&lt;=2^31，1&lt;=每个砝码的质量&lt;=2^30</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}